never around.

15:18.318 --> 15:19.852
Also can we not
talk about parents?

15:19.854 --> 15:21.520
I swear besides
Benji and statistics,

15:21.522 --> 15:22.787
that's
your favorite subject.

15:22.789 --> 15:24.656
Is Benji coming?

15:24.658 --> 15:26.191
See?

15:26.193 --> 15:27.059
[ Laughs ]

15:27.061 --> 15:28.694
I thought
that was the group.

15:30.197 --> 15:33.298
