just going to be you and me.

15:34.869 --> 15:35.868
Alright. Okay.

15:35.870 --> 15:39.804
Let's get started.

15:39.806 --> 15:43.141
[ Sighs ]

15:43.143 --> 15:45.143
These are clean.

15:45.145 --> 15:48.280
Uh, this top drawer
should be empty.

15:48.282 --> 15:49.548
It is.

15:49.550 --> 15:54.152
You can... you know,
put your stuff in there.

15:54.154 --> 15:58.690
You don't
have to do that.

15:58.692 --> 16:00.625
You need clean sheets.

16:00.627 --> 16:02.728
Everybody needs
clean sheets.

16:04.631 --> 16:06.231
I don't want
to mess things up for you.

16:07.701 --> 16:10.302
Just forget her, okay?

16:10.304 --> 16:13.472
She doesn't get to say
how things are supposed to be.

16:16.977 --> 16:18.042
Julia always said

16:18.044 --> 16:19.844
how much you worried
about Smurf,

16:19.846 --> 16:21.780
how you took care of her.

16:21.782 --> 16:24.182
She didn't blame you
for anything, you know.

16:24.184 --> 16:28.386
♪♪

16:28.388 --> 16:29.854
She understood
why you stayed here.

16:29.856 --> 16:34.859
♪♪

16:34.861 --> 16:36.328
Hey.

16:36.330 --> 16:38.797
