16:38.799 --> 16:41.533
I understand you, too.

16:41.535 --> 16:48.540
♪♪

16:48.542 --> 16:50.809
I... I give you a ride
to work when you're ready.

16:50.811 --> 16:53.011
[ Inhales shakily ]

16:53.013 --> 16:58.883
♪♪

16:58.885 --> 17:04.556
