17:07.762 --> 17:08.861
Craig: Hey.

17:11.298 --> 17:15.768
[ Bag rustles ]

17:15.770 --> 17:17.269
Do I need to count it?

17:21.642 --> 17:23.474
Okay.

17:25.311 --> 17:26.979
210.

17:26.981 --> 17:30.482
[ Exhales sharply ]

17:32.853 --> 17:36.388
That's 150 grand
less than we agreed on.

17:36.390 --> 17:37.522
I spoke to Raul.

17:37.524 --> 17:39.724
He needs a couple of weeks
to get the balance,

17:39.726 --> 17:41.660
so I negotiated.

17:41.662 --> 17:43.662
What are you talking about?
Another job.

17:43.664 --> 17:45.864
I'm not working
for that asshole again.

17:45.866 --> 17:47.932
This one could be bigger. No.

17:47.934 --> 17:49.802
Listen,
Raul's an important client

17:49.804 --> 17:51.870
of another
one of my partners, and I...

17:51.872 --> 17:53.137
Waiter Duane: Wine list?

17:53.139 --> 17:55.674
Later, man.

17:55.676 --> 17:57.009
Sure.

17:59.413 --> 18:02.347
Don't step over dollars
to pick up dimes.

18:02.349 --> 18:03.816
This is the long game.

18:03.818 --> 18:05.083
Play it.
Bullshit.

18:05.085 --> 18:07.886
Calm down.
You short me 150 grand,

18:07.888 --> 18:09.688
then you expect me
to "calm down"?

18:09.690 --> 18:11.356
We're professionals.

18:11.358 --> 18:13.758
There are other, more lucrative
opportunities coming.

18:13.760 --> 18:15.494
Screw that shit.

18:15.496 --> 18:17.562
Professionals get paid.

18:17.564 --> 18:24.302
♪♪

18:24.304 --> 18:31.043
♪♪

18:34.447 --> 18:35.647
So you only get an anomaly

18:35.649 --> 18:37.483
when the p value
is less than 0.5%.

18:39.052 --> 18:41.252
Cool.
Well, uh, I am done.

18:41.254 --> 18:42.321
[ Chuckles ]

18:42.323 --> 18:45.324
Yeah, I should probably
get going, too.

18:45.326 --> 18:50.261
[ Chuckles ]
Are you... a virgin, Josh?

18:50.263 --> 18:51.262
What do you mean?

18:51.264 --> 18:53.332
I'm asking you
if you've had sex before

18:53.334 --> 18:54.933
because if the answer's yes,

18:54.935 --> 18:57.268
I truly don't know
how that happened.

18:57.270 --> 19:00.005
[ The Years' "The Fear" plays ]

19:00.007 --> 19:05.210
♪ We've got no alibi, yeah ♪

19:05.212 --> 19:11.416
