19:16.289 --> 19:21.026
♪ We all, we all,
we all caught the fear ♪

19:21.028 --> 19:23.428
[ Moaning softly ]

19:23.430 --> 19:25.497
Meredith:
Three bottles of the...

19:25.499 --> 19:26.832
Sophia:
[ Speaks indistinctly ]

19:26.834 --> 19:28.967
Jesus, Mom!

19:28.969 --> 19:31.436
My fault.
Should have texted.

19:31.438 --> 19:33.438
We just got back.

19:33.440 --> 19:34.639
Who's this?

19:34.641 --> 19:36.307
I'm... I'm Josh.

19:36.309 --> 19:40.712
And this is my mom, Meredith,
and her assistant Sophia.

19:40.714 --> 19:42.914
Hello. The pleasure is all mine.

19:42.916 --> 19:46.117
Well, not <i> all</i> mine,
apparently.

19:46.119 --> 19:48.119
J's helping me
with statistics.

19:48.121 --> 19:49.320
[ Chuckles ]

19:49.322 --> 19:52.991
I'm gonna pretend
that's what we just saw.

19:52.993 --> 19:55.594
Forget we're even here.
We've got work to do.

19:55.596 --> 19:58.263
♪ Ripe for the taking ♪

19:58.265 --> 20:02.601
I thought you said
that she was away.

20:02.603 --> 20:05.537
Trust me, she's forgotten
about it already.

20:05.539 --> 20:06.605
♪♪

20:06.607 --> 20:08.874
Are you coming?

20:08.876 --> 20:13.545
♪ We all, we all,
we all caught the fear ♪

20:13.547 --> 20:15.447
♪ Unless we take control ♪

20:18.018 --> 20:22.353
Hey, uh, Tony Montana,
what's this?

20:22.355 --> 20:24.756
You get a job as a waiter
or something?

20:24.758 --> 20:25.691
[ Sniffs ]

20:25.693 --> 20:27.492
What?

20:27.494 --> 20:28.827
No.

20:30.497 --> 20:32.631
Sorry, look, uh...

20:32.633 --> 20:35.701
[ Clears throat ]

20:35.703 --> 20:37.569
I got this girl
to come out on this job,

20:37.571 --> 20:38.637
and she just stiffed me,

20:38.639 --> 20:40.439
and she's gonna make me
look like an asshole

20:40.441 --> 20:41.440
in front of
my brothers.

20:41.442 --> 20:42.841
What girl?

20:42.843 --> 20:44.309
[ Sniffs ]

20:44.311 --> 20:45.911
I really don't want to talk about it.
[ Scoffs ]

20:45.913 --> 20:47.512
Yeah, well, your brothers
already know you're an asshole,

20:47.514 --> 20:49.514
so you're fine.

20:49.516 --> 20:50.982
[ Sighs ]

20:50.984 --> 20:53.252
I can't believe
I trusted her.

20:53.254 --> 20:55.254
[ Sniffs ]

20:55.256 --> 20:58.123
You slept with her,
right?

20:58.125 --> 21:00.525
What?

21:00.527 --> 21:02.528
Was she at least
good in bed?

21:05.266 --> 21:06.198
Yeah.

21:07.868 --> 21:10.802
It wasn't about the sex, alright?
[ Laughs ]

21:10.804 --> 21:12.337
Sure. Mm-hmm.

21:12.339 --> 21:14.873
It wasn't just
about the sex.

21:14.875 --> 21:16.075
If you say so.

21:16.077 --> 21:17.543
[ Smooches ]

21:19.012 --> 21:21.947
You're an idiot.

21:21.949 --> 21:23.815
Yep.

21:23.817 --> 21:28.553
♪♪

21:28.555 --> 21:30.555
[ Metal banging ]

21:30.557 --> 21:37.362
♪♪

21:37.364 --> 21:43.969
♪♪

21:43.971 --> 21:46.505
[ Metal clatters ]

21:46.507 --> 21:54.245
♪♪

21:54.247 --> 21:56.581
It's a mess in here.

21:56.583 --> 21:58.851
Nothing's where
it's supposed to be.

22:01.588 --> 22:03.989
Everybody dies, baby.

22:03.991 --> 22:09.460
♪♪

22:09.462 --> 22:12.197
You think I care?

22:12.199 --> 22:20.739
♪♪

22:20.741 --> 22:22.874
The day you die

22:22.876 --> 22:25.877
will be the happiest day
of my life.

22:25.879 --> 22:33.885
♪♪

22:33.887 --> 22:36.488
[ Sighs ]

22:36.490 --> 22:41.426
♪♪

22:41.428 --> 22:44.029
Angela: [ Sighs ]

22:44.031 --> 22:49.168
♪♪

22:49.170 --> 22:51.103
Hey.

22:56.510 --> 22:57.609
What's wrong?

22:59.000 --> 23:05.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

23:08.589 --> 23:10.522
She's sick, right?

23:13.794 --> 23:15.660
What's she got?

23:15.662 --> 23:17.662
♪♪

23:17.664 --> 23:19.664
[ Quietly ] Hey.

23:19.666 --> 23:29.274
♪♪

23:29.276 --> 23:38.817
♪♪

23:38.819 --> 23:48.427
♪♪

23:48.429 --> 23:52.697
[ Both exhaling sharply ]

23:52.699 --> 23:55.500
I'm gonna close the door.

23:55.502 --> 24:02.373
♪♪

24:02.375 --> 24:08.980
♪♪

24:08.982 --> 24:10.649
[ Whispering ] We have
to be quiet, okay?

24:10.651 --> 24:12.117
Okay.

24:12.119 --> 24:18.523
♪♪

24:18.525 --> 24:20.693
Angela: [ Moans softly ]

24:25.732 --> 24:27.132
Good morning.

24:27.134 --> 24:29.134
There's coffee.

24:29.136 --> 24:30.936
Uh, I was just gonna get
some water, if that's okay.

24:30.938 --> 24:32.871
Sure. Help yourself.

24:35.943 --> 24:39.678
So, Olivia says
you are smart.

24:39.680 --> 24:41.880
What are you studying?

24:41.882 --> 24:43.548
I'm undeclared.

24:43.550 --> 24:45.684
Business, Pre-Law,
Civil Law, maybe.

24:45.686 --> 24:46.685
I'm not sure.

24:46.687 --> 24:48.921
There's no need to kiss ass,
Josh.

24:50.557 --> 24:52.424
Well, lawyers make
a lot of money, right?

24:52.426 --> 24:53.892
Eh,
lawyers make good money.

24:53.894 --> 24:57.629
Business people
make real money.

24:57.631 --> 24:58.830
What are you working on?

24:58.832 --> 25:05.436
An artist amenities inventory
for a show I have coming up.

25:05.438 --> 25:07.106
Exciting, huh?

25:07.108 --> 25:10.509
I don't know.
What is it?

25:10.511 --> 25:12.177
The headliner stipulates

25:12.179 --> 25:14.445
certain items
they want in their buses.

25:14.447 --> 25:16.181
Like green M&Ms?

25:16.183 --> 25:21.186
Try diamond tennis bracelets,
50 grand in ones.

25:21.188 --> 25:24.856
Then there are the laptops,
the equipment.

25:24.858 --> 25:28.727
A million-five
for this event.

25:28.729 --> 25:29.795
Wow.

25:29.797 --> 25:31.797
So the insurance company
needs an inventory list

25:31.799 --> 25:33.198
and a security plan.

25:33.200 --> 25:35.667
[ Exhales sharply ]

25:35.669 --> 25:37.602
You know,
if you're really interested,

25:37.604 --> 25:40.071
I'll be running the whole thing
out of the office here,

25:40.073 --> 25:42.073
and I am always looking
for smart people.

25:42.075 --> 25:44.476
Sure. Yeah.

25:44.478 --> 25:45.477
Thank you.

25:45.479 --> 25:47.346
Okay.

25:51.685 --> 25:52.551
Josh?

25:54.621 --> 25:56.621
I hope you're a nice guy.

25:56.623 --> 26:00.025
I know it doesn't
look like it, but...

26:00.027 --> 26:02.161
Olivia hasn't
had it easy.

26:02.163 --> 26:10.902
♪♪

26:10.904 --> 26:11.970
[ Rock music playing ]

26:11.972 --> 26:13.905
Hey, there he is.

26:13.907 --> 26:15.240
[ Cheers and applause ]

26:15.242 --> 26:16.775
Whoo!

26:16.777 --> 26:18.643
Let's go!

26:18.645 --> 26:20.779
[ All cheering, chanting ]

26:20.781 --> 26:23.314
Congratulations.
Congratulations.

26:23.316 --> 26:25.250
Thank you.
Thank you.

26:25.252 --> 26:28.453
- Yeah.
- Whoo!

26:28.455 --> 26:29.788
And they're all here
for you.

26:29.790 --> 26:31.190
Go on, man.

26:31.192 --> 26:38.129
[ All cheering ]

26:38.131 --> 26:41.867
[ Cheering continues ]

26:41.869 --> 26:45.804
Whoo! Whoo!

26:45.806 --> 26:52.211
[ All chanting "Adrian" ]

26:52.213 --> 26:57.883
[ Chanting continues ]

26:57.885 --> 26:59.918
- Let's go!
- Whoo!

27:03.891 --> 27:06.859
You didn't tell me
she could drive.

27:09.029 --> 27:10.896
You teach her that?

27:10.898 --> 27:12.264
Yo, hurry up.

27:21.108 --> 27:22.841
Janine's got an idea
for a job.

27:22.843 --> 27:24.243
What do you think, boss?

27:24.245 --> 27:26.245
I think you should
talk less and work more.

27:28.649 --> 27:30.181
Hey.

27:30.183 --> 27:32.117
Tell 'em.

27:32.119 --> 27:34.185
Tell 'em.

27:34.187 --> 27:37.188
There's a hippie compound
out in Laguna Beach.

27:37.190 --> 27:39.991
They're smuggling Thai Sticks
and making acid,

27:39.993 --> 27:41.192
a lot of it.

27:41.194 --> 27:45.264
So they're sitting on
a ton of cash.

27:45.266 --> 27:47.466
Should be easy.

27:51.338 --> 27:53.138
We do banks.

27:53.140 --> 27:54.873
Maybe we try
something different?

27:54.875 --> 27:56.909
We are trying
something different.

28:02.816 --> 28:04.917
If you've got something to say,
then just say it.

28:06.820 --> 28:08.419
I'm not new at this.

28:08.421 --> 28:09.288
You are.

28:09.290 --> 28:11.222
♪♪

28:11.224 --> 28:12.357
And you should
know better.

28:12.359 --> 28:20.565
♪♪

28:20.567 --> 28:30.375
[ Ringing ]

28:30.511 --> 28:40.519
[ Ringing continues ]

28:40.521 --> 28:43.655
♪♪

28:43.657 --> 28:45.524
[ Door closes ]

28:45.526 --> 28:53.799
♪♪

28:53.801 --> 28:55.467
What do you want?

28:55.469 --> 28:57.402
I have something
for you.

28:57.404 --> 28:58.337
[ Scoffs ]

28:58.339 --> 29:00.271
May I sit?
Sure.

29:00.273 --> 29:04.276
Forgot how nice
it was out here.

29:13.687 --> 29:15.354
That's a lot of money,
baby.

29:15.356 --> 29:18.357
In some circles.

29:18.359 --> 29:20.692
Why don't you tell me

29:20.694 --> 29:25.096
how dirt bag Billy's
ex-girlfriend shows up here

29:25.098 --> 29:26.965
and makes
such a grand entrance?

29:26.967 --> 29:28.900
Hm?

29:28.902 --> 29:31.636
Well, Billy was fun.

29:31.638 --> 29:34.840
He wouldn't shut up
about you.

29:34.842 --> 29:38.643
Billy wouldn't shut up
about anything.

29:38.645 --> 29:40.779
Well...

29:40.781 --> 29:44.783
I was interested
and impressed.

29:44.785 --> 29:45.985
That's your cut.

29:45.987 --> 29:47.919
From what?

29:47.921 --> 29:51.557
The job I just did
with the boys.

29:53.927 --> 29:56.728
My client
re-negotiated our fee.

29:56.730 --> 30:02.601
I accepted on the assurance
of more work in the future.

30:02.603 --> 30:05.070
Certainly, you see
the value of steady work,

30:05.072 --> 30:06.938
even if your boys don't.

30:06.940 --> 30:10.609
♪♪

30:10.611 --> 30:13.612
Craig should have told you
it's always better

30:13.614 --> 30:16.215
to approach me
for permission...

30:18.219 --> 30:20.752
not forgiveness.

30:20.754 --> 30:29.828
♪♪

30:29.830 --> 30:38.837
♪♪

30:42.442 --> 30:45.910
[ Rock music plays on radio ]

30:45.912 --> 30:48.913
[ Music, engine shuts off ]
Hey.

30:48.915 --> 30:52.517
Sorry I didn't see
your text.

30:52.519 --> 30:53.519
It's nice out.

31:04.465 --> 31:06.198
[ Jangles car keys ]

31:06.200 --> 31:08.033
[ Exhales sharply ]

31:12.339 --> 31:14.339
What are you doing?
You're staying?

31:14.341 --> 31:15.607
Yeah.

31:20.547 --> 31:22.347
Didn't Adrian
just get back?

31:22.349 --> 31:24.516
Yeah.

31:27.287 --> 31:28.753
Doesn't what's her face,
Roxy,

31:28.755 --> 31:30.022
mop at the end
of the night?

31:30.024 --> 31:32.557
It's my bar.
I can mop if I want to.

31:32.559 --> 31:34.759
Fine. Stay.

31:34.761 --> 31:35.694
Thanks.

31:35.696 --> 31:37.563
How's Smurf?

31:40.634 --> 31:41.900
Why?

31:41.902 --> 31:46.104
Apparently, she showed up
at Craig's doing shots

31:46.106 --> 31:50.776
and racking lines of coke
and Oxy, so...

31:52.246 --> 31:54.847
God, remember when Smurf
used to, like, really party?

31:54.849 --> 31:56.448
I think I was like
9 or 10.

31:56.450 --> 31:59.317
There was nothing
she wouldn't do...

31:59.319 --> 32:01.854
coke, speed, shrooms,
acid, weed.

32:01.856 --> 32:04.789
She was like
Hunter S. Thompson with tits.

32:04.791 --> 32:06.391
[ Chuckles ]

32:06.393 --> 32:07.992
And she had
that one dealer, Mike...

32:07.994 --> 32:10.062
Mark with the mullet.

32:10.064 --> 32:11.329
[ Chuckles ]

32:11.331 --> 32:13.265
You like stabbed him
with a fork

32:13.267 --> 32:15.400
while he was sleeping
in your bed.

32:15.402 --> 32:17.135
Mark.

32:17.137 --> 32:19.137
Prick.
Yeah.

32:19.139 --> 32:21.440
He was always
bothering Julia.

32:24.678 --> 32:27.279
It's just a little bit weird,
you know?

32:27.281 --> 32:29.214
She hasn't partied like that
in years,

32:29.216 --> 32:33.218
then she just shows up,
looking to get wasted.

32:33.220 --> 32:34.687
♪♪

32:34.689 --> 32:38.090
Hey.

32:38.092 --> 32:40.292
- Hey.
- Hey, Pope.

32:40.294 --> 32:41.826
Congratulations.

32:41.828 --> 32:44.162
Thanks.

32:44.164 --> 32:46.098
Thought maybe
you were surfing.

32:46.100 --> 32:49.101
No. Just been, uh,
cleaning up.

33:00.915 --> 33:03.715
Come on, Deran.

33:03.717 --> 33:04.950
What's up?

33:07.454 --> 33:09.321
I know you've been
moving shit for Jack.

33:09.323 --> 33:12.390
Come on, man.

33:12.392 --> 33:15.527
You had all the money
you needed with me.

33:15.529 --> 33:19.731
[ Swallows ] Yeah.

33:19.733 --> 33:21.600
Your money.

33:21.602 --> 33:23.668
Your house, your bar.

33:23.670 --> 33:26.605
That's how
you feel about this?

33:26.607 --> 33:28.406
Oh, so,
I can be your alibi,

33:28.408 --> 33:30.408
but I can't do something
on my own?

33:30.410 --> 33:31.476
No, you can.

33:31.478 --> 33:33.077
Just be smart about it

33:33.079 --> 33:35.680
because if you get caught,
that's 20 years in prison.

33:35.682 --> 33:38.050
Yeah, and that is my business,
so back off!

33:42.022 --> 33:43.221
Jesus!

33:43.223 --> 33:46.759
I just won
a four-star, man.

33:46.761 --> 33:48.994
You gonna take 10 seconds
and be happy for me?

33:50.564 --> 33:51.964
I'm sorry, man.
I should have told you.

33:51.966 --> 33:53.498
Stop.

33:53.500 --> 33:57.970
♪♪

33:57.972 --> 34:00.973
[ Chuckles nervously ]

34:00.975 --> 34:02.507
If you want to stop
taking money from me,

34:02.509 --> 34:04.009
that's fine.

34:05.579 --> 34:08.313
Just not from Jack, okay?

34:08.315 --> 34:09.848
The guy's careless.

34:09.850 --> 34:11.716
He's gonna get caught.

34:11.717 --> 34:14.585
♪♪

34:14.588 --> 34:16.054
You won it.

34:16.056 --> 34:19.190
Yeah.

34:19.193 --> 34:21.592
If I never do anything else
in my life, I did that.

34:21.594 --> 34:23.728
Come on.

34:23.730 --> 34:25.730
You're gonna win a lot more
than you just won.

34:25.732 --> 34:27.565
Come on.

34:32.005 --> 34:34.606
Deron: Look at you.
You're a pro-surfer now.

34:34.608 --> 34:36.475
I'm proud of you.

34:36.476 --> 34:38.275
♪♪

34:38.277 --> 34:40.145
Nothing's stock, man.

34:40.147 --> 34:43.081
Look, that's a great deal
on that bike.

34:43.083 --> 34:44.016
Huh?

34:44.018 --> 34:46.418
Okay. Tomorrow.

34:47.888 --> 34:50.222
Craigslist bullshit.

34:50.224 --> 34:51.690
Never gonna hear
from this asshole again.

34:51.692 --> 34:53.158
Why don't
you just tell them?

34:53.159 --> 34:55.694
Hey, look, let me...

34:55.696 --> 34:57.129
let me deal with this,
okay?

34:59.166 --> 35:03.769
Craig: Tidy up all this shit
later, alright?

35:10.644 --> 35:13.178
[ Exhales sharply ]

35:13.180 --> 35:14.312
Wow.

35:14.314 --> 35:16.648
It's just growing inside of ya,
huh?

35:16.650 --> 35:18.650
Like an alien.
Yeah.

35:18.652 --> 35:20.252
[ Laughing ]
Yeah, just like that.

35:23.323 --> 35:25.190
[ Exhales ]

35:25.192 --> 35:26.458
What's it feel like?

35:26.460 --> 35:30.328
Honestly, uh, feet hurt.

35:30.330 --> 35:31.396
I'm very horny.

35:31.398 --> 35:33.998
And all I want to eat
is Skittles.

35:34.000 --> 35:38.404
Well, I might be able
to help you out here.

35:45.212 --> 35:46.178
How is that?

35:49.950 --> 35:52.417
Okay. [ Laughs ]

35:52.419 --> 35:54.386
You know, I'm tapped out
on Skittles, but, um...

35:56.090 --> 35:57.489
So we should order a pizza,
then?

35:57.491 --> 35:59.892
Yeah, we could...

35:59.894 --> 36:02.427
Shit. [ Sighs ]

36:02.429 --> 36:04.963
I got lunch
at Smurf's later.

36:04.965 --> 36:07.366
Right.

36:07.368 --> 36:08.500
Yeah,
why don't you come?

36:09.970 --> 36:11.036
Oh, hell no.

36:17.111 --> 36:19.111
[ Sighs ]

36:19.113 --> 36:20.913
Alright.
See you in a couple days.

36:20.915 --> 36:22.181
[ Hangs up phone ]

36:29.590 --> 36:31.256
Alright.
[ Exhales ]

36:31.258 --> 36:33.525
There's a piece of property
in Crescent City.

36:33.527 --> 36:37.862
It's quiet, empty house,
barn, fresh water.

36:37.864 --> 36:41.466
Keys are underneath the rock
at the front gate.

36:41.468 --> 36:43.936
Yeah.

36:43.938 --> 36:45.403
I'm in.

36:45.405 --> 36:47.139
I got family
in Crescent City.

36:47.141 --> 36:48.540
Well, there you go.

36:48.542 --> 36:50.209
Bunch of speed freaks.

36:51.612 --> 36:54.479
Let's go south.

36:54.481 --> 36:56.415
There's plenty of banks.

36:56.417 --> 36:57.716
We can check out her job.

37:01.755 --> 37:03.889
You and Smurf decide
what jobs we're doing now?

37:05.760 --> 37:06.725
You the captain now?

37:08.228 --> 37:09.428
I got to take orders
from you.

37:11.298 --> 37:13.498
You want to go north, go.

37:13.500 --> 37:16.368
I'm tired of being cold.

37:23.778 --> 37:26.578
Okay. We go south.

37:32.319 --> 37:33.986
[ Quietly ]
We go south.

37:33.988 --> 37:43.127
♪♪

37:43.129 --> 37:44.729
Smurf:
Nice to see everybody

37:44.731 --> 37:47.666
still enjoys
a good barbeque, hm?

37:47.668 --> 37:54.006
You're not eating?

37:54.008 --> 37:57.676
We have something
we need to discuss.

38:00.547 --> 38:02.414
You all owe me money.

38:04.885 --> 38:09.621
From the job you pulled
with Frankie, remember?

38:09.623 --> 38:12.491
$50,000.
That's my cut.

38:12.493 --> 38:15.093
You have until tomorrow,
midnight.

38:15.095 --> 38:17.429
Is that going
to be a problem?

38:17.431 --> 38:20.699
Because word on the street is
you got shorted.

38:20.701 --> 38:22.167
Wait, what?

38:23.970 --> 38:25.570
What are you
looking at him for?

38:25.572 --> 38:27.639
It's all of you.

38:27.641 --> 38:32.377
You went against
everything I taught you.

38:32.379 --> 38:35.247
Jobs with outsiders?

38:35.249 --> 38:36.981
What are you,

38:36.983 --> 38:40.719
a crew that anybody could hire
and pay later?!

38:40.721 --> 38:47.659
♪♪

38:47.661 --> 38:49.194
Deran: When were you
gonna tell us

38:49.196 --> 38:50.863
that we didn't get
the rest of the money?

38:50.865 --> 38:52.064
We got paid, alright?

38:52.066 --> 38:54.399
Frankie was a little short,
but I'm good for it.

38:54.401 --> 38:57.001
J: How short?
Shut up.

38:57.003 --> 38:58.603
It was you,
wasn't it?

38:58.605 --> 39:01.406
What?
You told her.

39:01.408 --> 39:03.007
He didn't say shit.
Come on.

39:03.009 --> 39:03.942
Sure he did.

39:03.944 --> 39:05.410
Talking in your sleep.

39:05.412 --> 39:06.545
Smurf sitting next to you

39:06.547 --> 39:07.946
'cause you're afraid of
your bad dreams.

39:07.948 --> 39:09.748
Me? You're the one snorting
and screwing your way

39:09.750 --> 39:11.015
from one train wreck
to the next.

39:11.017 --> 39:12.217
Guys, come on.
Oh, yeah,

39:12.219 --> 39:13.351
because you've got it
all figured out

39:13.353 --> 39:14.553
living here with Mommy.
Craig.

39:14.555 --> 39:15.820
A couple more weeks,

39:15.822 --> 39:17.422
and she'll have you
back in diapers again.

39:17.424 --> 39:18.823
[ Shouts ]

39:18.825 --> 39:20.693
- Come on, man.
- Hey, hey!

39:20.695 --> 39:24.296
[ Both grunting ]

39:24.298 --> 39:25.531
Alright, alright, Craig.

39:27.301 --> 39:28.833
J: Come on.

39:28.835 --> 39:30.903
- Ho!
- Hey.

39:30.905 --> 39:32.571
Deran: Hey. Guys.

39:32.573 --> 39:34.306
- Come on!
- Break it up. Stop. Get off.

39:34.308 --> 39:36.174
Stop. Hey. Hey.

39:36.176 --> 39:37.776
Hey. Stop, stop, stop.

39:37.778 --> 39:39.511
Let's go find
this billionaire asshole

39:39.513 --> 39:40.979
and get our money back,
alright?

39:40.981 --> 39:42.047
Let's go. Come on.

39:46.320 --> 39:47.852
Come on.

39:47.854 --> 39:49.855
♪♪

39:53.260 --> 39:56.128
[ Indistinct conversations ]

39:56.130 --> 39:59.131
Adrian, hey. Sit down.

39:59.133 --> 40:00.532
[ Clears throat ]

40:00.534 --> 40:01.934
Oh, hey.
Congratulations, by the way.

40:01.936 --> 40:03.135
What?

40:03.137 --> 40:05.604
Oh, uh,
yeah, thank you.

40:05.606 --> 40:07.005
Don't thank me yet.

40:07.007 --> 40:08.140
[ Chuckles ]

40:08.142 --> 40:09.474
So next steps...

40:09.476 --> 40:12.077
prosecutor's office is
scheduling a deposition.

40:12.079 --> 40:14.212
Now there's gonna be
an initial hearing,

40:14.214 --> 40:18.416
then a trial,
then a sentencing hearing.

40:18.418 --> 40:21.153
You said I would have immunity
from prosecution if I cooperated?

40:21.155 --> 40:23.488
We're recommending a greatly reduced
sentence based on the guideline,

40:23.490 --> 40:24.689
but that's up to a judge.

40:24.691 --> 40:25.890
Now there's
a state detective

40:25.892 --> 40:27.025
that wants to ask you
a few questions.

40:27.027 --> 40:28.827
That wasn't
our agreement.

40:31.165 --> 40:33.766
Well, if it was me that was
appearing before a federal judge

40:33.768 --> 40:35.634
with the kind of prison time
your crime carries

40:35.636 --> 40:38.036
and an overworked public
defender standing next to me,

40:38.038 --> 40:39.571
I would want to look like
a team player.

40:41.375 --> 40:43.308
That's just me.

40:43.310 --> 40:44.309
[ Chuckles ]

40:44.311 --> 40:45.444
Sit tight.

40:46.781 --> 40:48.180
[ Door closes ]

40:48.182 --> 40:50.849
♪♪

40:50.851 --> 40:53.518
Dennis:
[ Laughs in distance ]

40:53.520 --> 40:55.454
♪♪

40:55.456 --> 40:58.256
Pearce: Mr. Dolan.

40:58.258 --> 41:01.393
I'm Detective Pearce,

41:01.395 --> 41:05.263
and I'm here just to ask you
a few questions

41:05.265 --> 41:07.800
about Deran Cody.

41:07.802 --> 41:09.267
Yeah, that's great.

41:09.269 --> 41:11.069
All right.
Thanks.

41:11.071 --> 41:20.679
♪♪

41:20.681 --> 41:22.614
[ Engine starts, revs ]

41:22.616 --> 41:24.949
♪♪

41:24.951 --> 41:26.418
Rahul's on the move.

41:26.420 --> 41:27.752
About damn time.

41:27.754 --> 41:29.554
[ Engine starts, revs ]

41:29.556 --> 41:34.893
♪♪

41:34.895 --> 41:40.365
♪♪

41:40.367 --> 41:42.901
You've been gone a lot.

41:42.903 --> 41:46.971
Yeah, I've been
working on some leads.

41:46.973 --> 41:49.974
That's good.

41:49.976 --> 41:53.245
Smurf can't bring us jobs
forever.

41:53.247 --> 41:56.648
♪♪

41:56.650 --> 41:58.851
She's getting old.

41:58.853 --> 42:05.257
♪♪

42:05.259 --> 42:12.264
[ Engines rev ]

42:12.266 --> 42:18.403
♪♪

42:18.405 --> 42:19.872
Craig:
<i>Coming to you now.</i>

42:19.874 --> 42:29.013
♪♪

42:29.015 --> 42:38.223
♪♪

42:38.225 --> 42:47.366
♪♪

42:47.368 --> 42:56.508
♪♪

42:56.510 --> 42:58.077
[ Tires squeal ]

43:06.387 --> 43:08.520
[ Engines shut off ]

43:08.522 --> 43:10.655
[ Breathing heavily ]

43:10.657 --> 43:12.324
Rahul:
You could have killed me.

43:12.326 --> 43:13.592
I think it's broken.

43:13.594 --> 43:14.659
Call an ambulance.

43:14.661 --> 43:16.929
No. No.

43:16.931 --> 43:18.530
You son of a bitch.

43:18.532 --> 43:20.532
Are you joking?

43:20.534 --> 43:22.601
Your watch.

43:22.603 --> 43:23.535
What?

43:23.537 --> 43:25.670
Your watch.

43:25.672 --> 43:26.671
Now. Let's go.

43:26.673 --> 43:28.673
Let's go.

43:28.675 --> 43:30.175
Put in the helmet.

43:32.679 --> 43:34.412
Pay your bills, shithead.

43:34.414 --> 43:35.747
♪♪

43:35.749 --> 43:41.019
[ Engines rev ]

43:41.021 --> 43:44.690
[ Tires squeal ]

43:51.766 --> 43:53.966
[ Water running ]

43:53.968 --> 43:55.167
[ Water shuts off ]

43:58.305 --> 44:01.373
Is there something wrong
with me having an idea?

44:01.375 --> 44:04.443
I know what you're doing here,
and I ain't cool with it.

44:04.445 --> 44:07.379
I'm... here
for the money.

44:07.381 --> 44:10.382
I don't know
what your deal is.

44:10.384 --> 44:13.118
This is my crew, Smurf.

44:13.120 --> 44:16.455
You're here
because I say so.

44:16.457 --> 44:21.726
♪♪

44:21.728 --> 44:24.062
I'm not sure that's true.

44:24.064 --> 44:33.271
♪♪

44:33.273 --> 44:42.481
♪♪

44:42.483 --> 44:43.948
Could you do the cash drop
tonight?

44:43.950 --> 44:45.283
Sure.

44:45.285 --> 44:49.888
♪♪

44:49.890 --> 44:51.089
Tupi: [ Grunts ]

44:51.091 --> 44:52.691
Come on, badass.
Get up.

44:52.693 --> 44:54.226
[ Grunts ]

44:54.228 --> 44:55.093
♪♪

44:55.095 --> 44:56.961
[ Shouts ]

44:56.963 --> 44:58.497
[ Both grunting ]

44:58.499 --> 45:03.968
♪♪

45:03.970 --> 45:09.174
♪♪

45:09.176 --> 45:13.712
[ Breathing heavily ]

45:15.049 --> 45:23.121
♪♪

